	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratissima mihi occasio fuit, qua respondere tuis possem, et primum, quod pecuniam attinet <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l378" cert="high">Lutetiam</placeName> transmittendam, scias nihildum esse effectum, quia hactenus <persName type="citizen_name">Iacobus ille de Puteo</persName> non venit; sed ita disposui omnia, ut, si veniat, mox indicetur.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Comitem se illi adiunget <persName type="auto_name">Kelleri</persName> frater, aurifaber, qui uxoris meae fratri servit, iuvenis satis egregius.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De bello inter <placeName type="citizen_name">Ianuenses</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name">Gallos</placeName> longe secus nos accipimus, hoc est <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Galli</placeName> classem 20 navibus constantem tempestatis vi esse demersam duabus tantum exceptis galeis, tum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2801" cert="high">Corsicam</placeName> a <placeName type="citizen_name">Ianuensibus</placeName> recuperatam praeter arcem S. Dionysii, quam inexpugnabilem aiunt, eoque successu adeo crevisse animos Caesari, ut legatum pontificium pacis nescio quas conditiones adferentem penitus sit aversatus.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed et novam quandam insulam ab <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanis</placeName> repertam eamque mineris auri argentique divitem.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De connubio inter <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanum</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglam</placeName> pacta et conclusa omnia nunciantur iisque conditionibus hoc ipsum coiisse, ut <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Angliae</placeName> maneat salva gubernationis antiquae forma autoritasque senatus parlamentarii, cui tamen interesse et ipse princeps, si velit, queat; <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanos</placeName> non plures quinquaginta in insula foveat et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l20" cert="high">Germaniam Inferiorem</placeName> sive liberis ex regina relinquat, sive sine herede decedat, regno Anglico subdat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Artes hae sunt <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanicę</placeName> vulpibus capiendis destinatae.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Verum eas aerumnas meretur prodigiosa populi ingratitudo et inconstantia.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8371" cert="high">Albertus</persName> aliquot adhuc vexilla habet reliqua militum in oppido <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1031" cert="high">Swinfurt</placeName> et <placeName type="auto_name">Blassemburg</placeName> incolume et utrobique nervum belli<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Vgl. <hi>Cicero,</hi> Orationes Philippicae, 5, 5 und s. <bibl>HBBW</bibl> XIV *** .</note> tantum cum aliis necessariis, quae pro ducendo in longum bello sufficiant.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De pace acturi dicuntur confoederati (quos vocant) <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l210" cert="high">Heidelbergenses</placeName>, sed citra magnam spem successus.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De comitiis nihil sicut nec de concilio.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Lycosthenes noster ecclesiarum adiutus precibus nonnihil respirare cępit et iam lingua balbutit, qui et literas tuas, quas ipse exhibui, magna animi refectione perlegit et per me tibi gratias agi cupivit.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale in domino, vir ornatissime, cum tuis omnibus.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileae</placeName> 7. ianuarii anno 1554.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3099" cert="high">Sulcerus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Viro praestantissimo d. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Heinricho Bullingero</persName>, domino et symmistae suo colendissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="attachment">[Notiz von <persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Bullingers</persName> Hand:]</note>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Misit <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18554" cert="high">regina Angliae</persName> 9 naves onerarias in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispaniam</placeName> una cum suo legato evocatum sponsum, qui ad futurum ver forte in martio venturus putatur.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interim 20. decembris proclamavit sub poena capitis, ne quisquam loquatur palam de nuptiis <placeName type="auto_name">Caesareanis</placeName> aut <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanicis</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
